    "chemicalDescription": [
      "r-(sh-Polypeptide-19 Decapeptide-40) is a single chain recombinant peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the genes encoding for sh-Polypeptide-19 and Decapeptide-40. The fusion peptide contains 60 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
